          <h1 id="miniconda">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#miniconda"></a>
miniconda
</h1><h2 id="1-配置">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%ae"></a>
1. 配置
</h2><p>环境变量:
![[Pasted image 20260520012222.png]]</p>
<p>生成.condarc文件:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">conda init cmd.exe
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">conda config --set show_channel_urls yes		//生成.condarc文件
</span></span></code></pre></div><p>替换.condarc文件:</p>
<div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">channels:
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - defaults
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">show_channel_urls: true
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">default_channels:
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/main
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/r
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  - https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/pkgs/msys2
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">custom_channels:
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  conda-forge: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  msys2: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  bioconda: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  menpo: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  pytorch: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  pytorch-lts: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  simpleitk: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  deepmodeling: https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/anaconda/cloud/
</span></span></code></pre></div><h1 id="命令">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%91%bd%e4%bb%a4"></a>
命令
</h1><h2 id="1-基本命令">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e5%9f%ba%e6%9c%ac%e5%91%bd%e4%bb%a4"></a>
1. 基本命令
</h2><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-powershell" data-lang="powershell"><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">conda</span> <span class="n">env</span> <span class="n">list</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">conda</span> <span class="n">create</span> <span class="p">-</span><span class="n">-name</span> <span class="n">名字</span> <span class="n">python</span><span class="p">=</span><span class="mf">3.11</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="py">5</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">conda</span> <span class="n">create</span> <span class="n">-n</span> <span class="n">名字</span> <span class="n">python</span><span class="p">=</span><span class="mf">3.10</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="py">9</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">conda</span> <span class="n">create</span> <span class="p">-</span><span class="n">-clone</span> <span class="n">名字</span> <span class="p">-</span><span class="n">-name</span> <span class="n">新名字</span>	<span class="p">//</span><span class="n">克隆一个一模一样的环境</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="n">conda</span> <span class="n">remove</span> <span class="p">-</span><span class="n">-name</span> <span class="n">名字</span> <span class="p">-</span><span class="n">-all</span>
