    <item>
      <title>[工具] AutoHotkey</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/autohotkey/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 00:00:00 &#43;0000</pubDate>
      <author>xxx@example.com (byzh)</author>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/post/%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/autohotkey/</guid>
      <description>
        <![CDATA[<h1>[工具] AutoHotkey</h1><p>作者：byzh（xxx@example.com）</p>
        
          <h1 id="基础">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%9f%ba%e7%a1%80"></a>
基础
</h1><h4 id="1-界面">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#1-%e7%95%8c%e9%9d%a2"></a>
1. 界面
</h4><p>window spy: 窗口间谍</p>
<h4 id="2-快捷键">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#2-%e5%bf%ab%e6%8d%b7%e9%94%ae"></a>
2. 快捷键
</h4><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">^ = Ctrl
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">+ = Shift
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"># = Win
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">! = Alt
</span></span></code></pre></div><h1 id="全局快捷键">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%85%a8%e5%b1%80%e5%bf%ab%e6%8d%b7%e9%94%ae"></a>
全局快捷键
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">^m::
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">{
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    backup := A_Clipboard
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    A_Clipboard := &#34;&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    Send &#34;^c&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    if !ClipWait(1)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    {
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        A_Clipboard := backup
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        return
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    text := A_Clipboard
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    SendText &#34;&lt;mark&gt;&#34; text &#34;&lt;/mark&gt;&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    A_Clipboard := backup
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">}
</span></span></code></pre></div><h1 id="指定软件快捷键">
<a class="header-anchor" href="#%e6%8c%87%e5%ae%9a%e8%bd%af%e4%bb%b6%e5%bf%ab%e6%8d%b7%e9%94%ae"></a>
指定软件快捷键
</h1><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">#HotIf WinActive(&#34;ahk_exe Typora.exe&#34;) || WinActive(&#34;ahk_exe Obsidian.exe&#34;)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">; 仅当 XX 窗口处于激活状态时，下面的热键才生效
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">^m::
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">{
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    backup := A_Clipboard
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ; 备份当前剪贴板内容，防止覆盖用户原有数据
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    A_Clipboard := &#34;&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ; 清空剪贴板，确保后续 Ctrl+C 能正确触发内容变化
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    Send &#34;^c&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ; 模拟按下 Ctrl+C，复制当前选中的文本
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    if !ClipWait(1)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    {
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        ; 等待剪贴板更新，最多 1 秒
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        ; 如果超时（没有成功复制内容）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        A_Clipboard := backup
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        ; 恢复原剪贴板内容
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        return
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        ; 直接退出
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    }
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    text := A_Clipboard
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ; 获取刚刚复制的文本内容
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    SendText &#34;&lt;mark&gt;&#34; text &#34;&lt;/mark&gt;&#34;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ; 在当前输入位置输出 HTML 高亮标签包裹的文本
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    A_Clipboard := backup
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ; 恢复原剪贴板内容，避免污染用户剪贴板
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">}
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">#HotIf
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">; 结束条件限制作用域
</span></span></code></pre></div>
        
        <hr><p>本文2026-05-19首发于<a href='http://localhost:1313/'>byzh的博客</a>，最后修改于2026-05-19</p>]]>
